{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[null],"uses":{}},{"type":"data","data":[{"title":1,"url":2,"footer":3,"image":3,"publicationDate":4,"active":5,"meta":6,"header":11,"lastUpdatedOn":12,"content":13,"scripts":3},"About","/about","",1732233600000,true,{"title":7,"keywords":8,"description":9,"structured":3,"og":10},"About Genos: Leading the Way in Innovative Scientific Solutions for Research and Industry","Genos, scientific solutions, innovative research tools, commercial scientific solutions, research innovation, scientific discovery, advanced technologies, industry solutions, research and industry, scientific advancements","Learn about Genos, a pioneer in delivering innovative scientific solutions for research and industry. Discover how our advanced technologies are shaping the future of scientific discovery and commercial success.",{"image":3},"lpl-cOnqSF3nbMMpJusnJgqAj8YA","2024-11-27T07:34:11.817Z","\u003Cpb-mobile-menu id=igqn labels=Home,About,Service,Projects,Publications links=/,/about,/services,/projects,/publications>\u003C/pb-mobile-menu>\u003Csection class=section>\u003Ch1 id=MfBKpH0Cc9BWbpbx class=\"h1 we-are-genos\">\u003Cspan id=Rgktne8zmGJGnCcG>We are \u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=zh6YUzpwbTuJI6aB>G\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=TcN59iN1gtU52Ey1>E\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=FRuvPjwKtHXbPYyE>N\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=zYA64bZk8loCkd4P>O\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=yhJ06x8lPrjG2YCr>S\u003C/span>\u003C/h1>\u003C/section>\u003Csection id=TZFy2cxsl8zlmE6w class=complex-section>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fblue-rectangle.svg?alt=media\" id=ELprkP97dG7EH6Ce class=complex-section-bg-image>\u003Cdiv id=lUHXTFZh0nKF19nt class=\"grid grid-large complex-section-grid\">\u003Ccolumn id=Uvpqpta2kAiwMVX4 class=gc-12>\u003Ch2 id=Ic5Xzo5xvin6Y5fB class=\"h2 complex-section-title\">\u003Cspan id=igwco>We are the largest glycan analysis lab \u003Cspan>\u003Cspan id=igwtq>in the world.\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/h2>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003C/section>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fgenos-building.png?alt=media\" id=i161o class=genos-building>\u003Csection id=iyi8a class=genos-about-section>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fblue-wave.svg?alt=media\" id=iv6ek class=genos-about-section-wave>\u003Cdiv id=ih1ff class=\"grid grid-large genos-about-section-grid\">\u003Ccolumn id=iedyd class=\"gc-8 gc-sm-10 gc-xs-12 gcs-4 gcs-sm-3 gcs-xs-1\">\u003Cp id=irx97>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=ir6ba>Our journey started in 2008 where we analyzed over 1,000 individuals from the Croatian island Vis. More than 10 years later we have published over 150 research publications and completed more than 20 collaborative projects with research and commercial facilities around the world.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>Today the laboratory has the capacity for 150,000+ glycan analyses per annum and represents the majority of the glycan research \u003Cb>in the world\u003C/b>.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fblue-triangle.svg?alt=media\" id=icl58 class=genos-about-section-triangle>\u003C/section>\u003Csection id=aQa0yO9fLVK9G9lb class=\"complex-section world-class-scientists spacer\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fhexagon.svg?alt=media\" id=mC01bPpJM1GLcTOS class=complex-section-bg-image>\u003Cdiv id=ZB2ykMQUKha5m0fa class=\"grid grid-large complex-section-grid\">\u003Ccolumn id=iCdmnOLVIRfKpf00 class=gc-9>\u003Ch2 id=HuaChmjvqno5aiel class=\"h2 complex-section-title\">\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=i5ojl>We are a team of world-class \u003Cspan>\u003Cspan id=igrrr>scientists\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/h2>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=bDgVT3IzKasrrE9r class=gc-3>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fhexagons.svg?alt=media\" id=95j0DEL1uFNLtoHW class=complex-section-image>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=m9X8i5FBz4Cxr6GA class=\"gc-8 gcs-4 gc-sm-10 gcs-sm-3 gc-xs-12 gcs-xs-1\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fquote.svg?alt=media\" id=idbhb class=gl-quote>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fgordan.png?alt=media\" id=icil1>\u003Ch3 id=i1d9g class=\"h3 gl-name\">\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=ibi2r>Prof. Gordan Lauc\u003C/span>\u003C/h3>\u003Ch5 id=iloax class=h5>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=i3yky>Founder &amp; CEO\u003C/span>\u003C/h5>\u003Cp id=idgqx class=gl-about>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=ivws5>Dr. Gordan Lauc is Professor of Biochemistry and Molecular Biology at the University of Zagreb Faculty of Pharmacy and Biochemistry and founder and CEO of Genos Ltd.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>He chaired a number of conferences, including the “European Science Foundation Exploratory Workshop on Glycoscience” which resulted in the creation of the “European Glycoscience Forum”.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>He is a President elect of the International Glycoscience Organization and member of the Steering Committee of the European Glycoscience Forum.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003C/section>\u003Cdiv id=dEn2uFiubT9QaQrw class=\"grid grid-large team spacer-small\">\u003Ccolumn id=yFChKG47jaHJIGuj class=\"gc-3 gc-sm-4 gc-xs-6\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fteam-member-placeholder.png?alt=media\" id=6k4KtgrkeXzOwU56 class=team-mem