.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fteam-member-placeholder.png?alt=media\" id=i31tnl class=team-member-img>\u003Ch3 class=\"h3 team-member-name\">\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=ikvcpi>Team Member Name\u003C/span>\u003C/h3>\u003Cspan class=team-member-title>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=ikzgsu>Team Member Title\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=igrib1 class=\"gc-3 gc-sm-4 gc-xs-6\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fteam-member-placeholder.png?alt=media\" id=i1opuy class=team-member-img>\u003Ch3 class=\"h3 team-member-name\">\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=iixxxc>Team Member Name\u003C/span>\u003C/h3>\u003Cspan class=team-member-title>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=i2ne14>Team Member Title\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=iycq35 class=\"gc-3 gc-sm-4 gc-xs-6\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fteam-member-placeholder.png?alt=media\" id=i330x4 class=team-member-img>\u003Ch3 class=\"h3 team-member-name\">\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=ihghlg>Team Member Name\u003C/span>\u003C/h3>\u003Cspan class=team-member-title>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=iki73n>Team Member Title\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=inpxsl class=\"gc-3 gc-sm-4 gc-xs-6\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fteam-member-placeholder.png?alt=media\" id=iywzo6 class=team-member-img>\u003Ch3 class=\"h3 team-member-name\">\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=ivitdm>Team Member Name\u003C/span>\u003C/h3>\u003Cspan class=team-member-title>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=ifmad2>Team Member Title\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=i2s0gk class=\"gc-3 gc-sm-4 gc-xs-6\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fteam-member-placeholder.png?alt=media\" id=ih9dnm class=team-member-img>\u003Ch3 class=\"h3 team-member-name\">\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=i8bod7>Team Member Name\u003C/span>\u003C/h3>\u003Cspan class=team-member-title>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=iyktnm>Team Member Title\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003Csection id=YA5FEVOEVWYCEXvO class=\"complex-section spacer\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fyellow-circle.svg?alt=media\" id=GLKC0v7KzHFjSfpF class=complex-section-bg-image>\u003Cdiv id=99t12REcY3UdZDUw class=\"grid grid-large complex-section-grid\">\u003Ccolumn id=MOMvkAGuSkXyzlxL class=gc-12>\u003Ch2 id=hs21csPYDrnEFdsG class=\"h2 complex-section-title\">\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=i62tld>We’re passionate about \u003Cspan>\u003Cspan id=iysz38>glycans\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/h2>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=ol0BM2fqEy2TjSZV class=\"gc-8 gcs-4 gc-sm-10 gcs-sm-3 gc-xs-12 gcs-xs-1\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fpassion.png?alt=media\" id=ir1idg class=passion>\u003Cp id=iks9qc>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=is1rqf>Glycans are the ultimate layer of complexity of life. These complex oligosaccharides change the struc-ture and function of proteins and other molecules.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>The level of molecular complexity achieved by glycosylation increases the proteome diversity to a level orders of magnitude greater than any other post-translational modification.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>Proteins depend on secondary modifications to maintain structural integrity and perform their fun-ction. Over half of all existing proteins are glycosyl-ated, the average mass representation of the maj-ority of proteins are glycans. All secreted proteins are glycosylated and can serve as biomarkers.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>Glycans are functional effectors in a variety of conditions, but also in autoimmune and chronic diseases. They are the biomarkers of inflammation and can prognose a variety of conditions.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fmisc%2Fblue-lines.svg?alt=media\" id=idearu>\u003C/section>\u003Csection id=BRK1ENKU47gsqxHg class=complex-section>\u003Cdiv id=lu6RgyxszVN9fh9A class=\"grid grid-large complex-section-grid\">\u003Ccolumn id=pZsfLecv3wkfHI0L class=gc-12>\u003Ch2 id=QTiVFd7WD6LgNXxH class=\"h2 complex-section-title\">\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=iocqcg>Our passion project: \u003Cspan>\u003Cspan id=i9vwlq>Human Glycome\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/h2>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fhuman-glycome.png?alt=media\" id=ijavxc class=glycan-chain>\u003Cdiv id=ioig2x class=\"grid grid-large\">\u003Ccolumn id=igtfu7 class=\"gc-9 gcs-4 gc-sm-12\">\u003Cp id=i4ixbk>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=isgks9>The Human Glycome Project is a research group that shares a common interest of defining the structures and functions of human glycome.\u003Cbr>It’s goal is in-depth understanding of the effect that glycans have in health and disease.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>Genos serves as the central hub in analysis of all human glycans.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003C/section>\u003Cdiv id=i2fola class=\"grid grid-large\">\u003Ccolumn id=9MiFxV1VrUEEumpz class=\"gc-12 cta-arrows\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-right-blue.svg?alt=media\" id=dH3AJJky8RByCcRw class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-right-blue.svg?alt=media\" id=QD3k1YDaaQQXfefq class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-right-blue.svg?alt=media\" id=atl0rMWdgUhjtl89 class=arrow-big>\u003Ca id=ip6cuv href=https://human-glycome.org/ target=_blank class=hover-underline>human-glycome.org\u003C/a>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-left-blue.svg?alt=media\" id=panBLNlsTxXEQekC class=arrow-big>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-left-blue.svg?alt=media\" id=agSwYeDGfhqZ1wxS class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-left-blue.svg?alt=media\" id=QatGefcauW3QoQA3 class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fmisc%2Fgreen-lines.svg?alt=media\" id=ib7y2y class=glycan-chain>\u003Csection id=QxEoDGRj8XIIJmT7 class=complex-section>\u003Cdiv id=IGJLBSqkr2je3xQU class=\"grid grid-large complex-section-grid from-science-to-product\">\u003Ccolumn id=YeBbQQSOxfxUcTeR class=gc-9>\u003Ch2 id=Ki38WEjEwrTvDEj7 class=\"h2 complex-section-title from-science-to-product-title\">\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=iimqwr>From science to product: \u003Cspan>\u003Cspan id=izkexo>GlycanAge\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/h2>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=J8mNKwmUc6gGtLJw class=gc-3>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Fabout%2Fkit.png?alt=media\" id=uX0uQP8XAFtUyi7t class=\"complex-section-image from-science-to-product-img\">\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=csbWHQFtkslPAvTn class=\"gc-8 gcs-4 gc-sm-10 gcs-sm-3 gc-xs-12 gcs-xs-1\">\u003Cp id=ilhfa8>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=i38duj>GlycanAge is a biological age testing kit (and a health improvement service). It does so through measuring number of pro and anti inflammatory glycans attached to IgG.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>It aims to help people increase the number of anti-inflammatory, and reduce number of pro-inflammatory glycans.\u003Cbr>\u003Cbr>Genos has researched glycans as a biomarker over the past 20 years, and now servers as the central hub for GlycanAge blood sample analysis.\u003C/span>\u003C/p>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003C/section>\u003Cdiv id=i6imn1 class=\"grid grid-large\">\u003Ccolumn id=N8MJ9hXMJingWa75 class=\"gc-12 cta-arrows\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-right-green.svg?alt=media\" id=UhkdOwaoY92aluuj class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-right-green.svg?alt=media\" id=sgoMmtnawQ4Jdow5 class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-right-green.svg?alt=media\" id=BskE9ebAKRZ09QoK class=arrow-big>\u003Ca data-pblink id=gjiUJpY6sRTyfbQK href=https://glycanage.com/ >\u003C/a>\u003Ca id=ixv4is href=https://glycanage.com/ target=_blank>glycanage.com\u003C/a>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-left-green.svg?alt=media\" id=WLa2EKU7yBFuiDW0 class=arrow-big>\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-left-green.svg?alt=media\" id=2hwekRwRk26wZ3BW class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003Cimg src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/genos-ec52a.firebasestorage.app/o/pages%2Farrows%2Farrow-left-green.svg?alt=media\" id=comjYKTbjRRspgXM class=\"arrow-big hide-xs\">\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003Csection id=MXTaHRlFxjZRA932 class=\"cta-request cta-about\">\u003Cdiv id=hUjO8q9BcuzBHclh class=\"grid grid-large cta-request-grid\">\u003Ccolumn id=IiQzJ4qLtjWt0RBn class=gc-12>\u003Ch2 id=FkEfBam5Q1ApeS8m class=\"h3 cta-request-text\">\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan>\u003C/span>\u003Cspan id=8zpGSuvni6nnOghJ>If you’re interested in working with us or using our services, submit a request for free and we’ll schedule a meeting to discuss your ideas.\u003C/span>\u003C/h2>\u003C/column>\u003Ccolumn id=RKT5fySTopITUNhl class=gc-12>\u003Ca data-pblink id=CFq5hFI6wJXPTkgx href=/request class=\"cta-big cta-yellow\">Submit free request\u003C/a>\u003C/column>\u003C/div>\u003C/section>\u003Cstyle>  #MfBKpH0Cc9BWbpbx{line-height:100%;text-align:center;color:black;}#yhJ06x8lPrjG2YCr{color:#ffd400;}#zYA64bZk8loCkd4P{color:#ff8000;}#FRuvPjwKtHXbPYyE{color:#80bf40;}#TcN59iN1gtU52Ey1{color:#40bfbf;}#zh6YUzpwbTuJI6aB{color:#4095bf;}#Rgktne8zmGJGnCcG{display:block;}#Ic5Xzo5xvin6Y5fB{max-width:14ch;color:#4095bf;}#igwco{white-space-collapse:preserve;color:black;}#igwtq{color:#4095bf;}#ELprkP97dG7EH6Ce{color:black;}#ir6ba{white-space-collapse:preserve;}#i5ojl{white-space-collapse:preserve;}#igrrr{color:#80bf40;}#idbhb{color:black;}#iloax{color:black;}#i1d9g{color:black;}#ibi2r{white-space-collapse:preserve;}#i3yky{white-space-collapse:preserve;}#ivws5{white-space-collapse:preserve;}#\\36 k4KtgrkeXzOwU56{color:black;}#OXWSR2XkelJmAFTG{white-space-collapse:preserve;}#bwHbViuIcXoPMklr{white-space-collapse:preserve;}#yUIpGCqxjvbjNazi{color:black;}#sRXkj5VBVzMpMsdb{white-space-collapse:preserve;}#wLZzm1XWGxwKuuY9{white-space-collapse:preserve;}#Sx2XhfjPKtwTCp9l{color:black;}#eZLqg9q1RpOaXSmV{white-space-collapse:preserve;}#Avo5Z5ORvCppjjML{w